column5: Hit Binbrook with DWC67,  punched a bunch of holes, but couldn't find any takers...  wind was howling something fierce, glad i had the hut...  Here's a pic od DWC67 doing some scouting
Sorry to hear you didn't get anything.  You had a much better chance at catchin something and me....I was on the couch all day...LOL.  You'll get em next time!
I guess it beats being at home and doing nothing, or some chores.
You should have gone to Cooks Bay... At least you got out.
